rows.label: qst702802_msg0001
rows.name:
Prince Adel! As result of steady and
unrelenting investigative spy activity of
Macmac, new info have come to light!

rows.label: qst702802_msg0002
rows.name:
From what Macmac gather, can still
find green barrels even within capital.
Shock horror, Macmac know!

rows.label: qst702802_msg0003
rows.name:
What worry Macmac is fact barrels
left out in broad daylight. Maybe part
of larger operation than first thought.

rows.label: qst702802_msg0004
rows.name:
Macmac ask Prince Adel to
exercise due caution.

rows.label: qst702802_msg0005
rows.name:
Dumdums who buy Red Pollen Orbs
also soon to be on receiving end of
Macmac's patented backwing slap!

rows.label: qst702802_msg0006
rows.name:
Will inform Prince Adel soon as
Macmac finds location of dumdum
dealer!

rows.label: qst702802_msg0007
rows.name:
Anypon who ruin peace of Iira
has wrath of Macmac to face!

rows.label: qst702802_msg0008
rows.name:
Will make spankings look like
least of dumdums' worries!

rows.label: qst702802_msg0101
rows.name:
Prince Adel! How goes retrieval
of Red Pollen Orbs?

rows.label: qst702802_msg0102
rows.name:
Macmac stay hot on heels of dumdums
who scatter Red Pollen Orbs around
like they not know any better!

rows.label: qst702802_msg0103
rows.name:
When friends almost done with cleanup
of Red Pollen Orbs in green barrels,
Macmac should have more to report!

rows.label: qst702802_msg0201
rows.name:
By the by, in course of investigation
into Red Pollen Orbs, Macmac hear
all sort of rumors about Prince Adel!

rows.label: qst702802_msg0202
rows.name:
All good, of course. Say how prince and
friends are wonderful people and so on.
Make Macmac happy to be acquainted!

rows.label: qst702802_msg0203
rows.name:
But for Macmac, this still not enough!
Is earnest wish that Prince Adel
spread love of justice to everyone!

rows.label: qst702802_msg0204
rows.name:
Is matter of course that in due time,
most if not all people in Iira and
Gula become fans of Team Adel!

rows.label: qst702802_msg0205
rows.name:
Also, if friends garner much attention,
make investigating in secret easier, so
it like two-Fliers-one-stone-type deal.

rows.label: qst702802_msg0206
rows.name:
Fate of everything is riding on
shoulders of friends. No pressure from
side of Macmac or anything!

rows.label: qst702802_msg0301
rows.name:
Hello, all! Sadly, investigation of
Macmac still take some more time.

rows.label: qst702802_msg0302
rows.name:
Friends should use time to go back to
Aurium and help other people in need.

rows.label: qst702802_msg0303
rows.name:
There many things that require friends'
expertise, like oasis, or build shelter, or
whatever is deal of that Invidian chap.

rows.label: qst702802_msg0304
rows.name:
Macmac strongly feel culprit in case is
someone who live in royal capital...
So please to cause stir and flush out!
